---
---

<div class="about-modal" id="about-modal" role="dialog" aria-modal="true" aria-labelledby="about-modal-title" hidden>
  <div class="about-backdrop" data-about-close></div>
  <div class="about-content" tabindex="-1">
    <button class="about-close" data-about-close aria-label="Close about panel">
      <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" aria-hidden="true">
        <path d="M18 6L6 18M6 6l12 12" />
      </svg>
    </button>

    <div class="about-body">
      <h2 id="about-modal-title" class="typo-display">Sam Stringer-Hye</h2>

      <p class="about-bio typo-body">
        Product designer at Razorfish with 10+ years across UI, UX, motion, and design systems. I've shipped work for Samsung, Frontier, and CVS. Mostly I obsess over the details most people scroll right past.
      </p>

      <p class="about-bio typo-body">
        I care a lot about craft. How a transition feels, whether the type hierarchy actually works, if a component holds up at every breakpoint. That stuff never shows up in a brief, but you always notice it in the final product.
      </p>

      <nav class="about-links" aria-label="Contact links">
        <a href="mailto:sam@samstringerhye.com" class="about-link typo-body">sam@samstringerhye.com</a>
        <a href="https://linkedin.com/in/samstringerhye" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="about-link typo-body">LinkedIn<span class="visually-hidden"> (opens in new tab)</span></a>
        <a href="/assets/resume.pdf" download class="about-link typo-body">Download Resume</a>
      </nav>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<style>
  .about-modal {
    position: fixed;
    inset: 0;
    z-index: var(--z-modal);
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
  }

  .about-modal[hidden] {
    display: none;
  }

  .about-backdrop {
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    background: var(--color-backdrop);
    backdrop-filter: blur(var(--modal-backdrop-blur));
    -webkit-backdrop-filter: blur(var(--modal-backdrop-blur));
  }

  .about-content {
    position: relative;
    width: 100%;
    max-width: var(--modal-max-width);
    max-height: var(--modal-max-height);
    background: var(--color-bg-primary);
    padding: var(--space-6) var(--space-5);
    overflow-y: auto;
    border-radius: var(--radius-3x);
    box-shadow: var(--modal-shadow);
  }

  .about-close {
    position: absolute;
    top: var(--space-4);
    right: var(--space-4);
    color: var(--color-text-secondary);
    transition: color var(--transition-fast) ease;
  }

  .about-close:hover {
    color: var(--color-text-primary);
  }

  .about-close svg {
    width: 3rem;
    height: 3rem;
  }

  .about-body {
    padding-top: var(--space-5);
  }

  .about-body h2 {
    margin-bottom: var(--space-3);
  }

  .about-bio {
    margin-bottom: var(--space-4);
  }

  .about-bio:last-of-type {
    margin-bottom: var(--space-5);
  }

  .about-links {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: var(--space-2);
  }

  @media (--2x) {
    .about-modal {
      align-items: stretch;
      justify-content: stretch;
    }

    .about-content {
      max-width: none;
      max-height: none;
      width: 100vw;
      min-height: 100dvh;
      margin: 0;
      border-radius: 0;
      padding:
        calc(var(--space-6) + env(safe-area-inset-top))
        var(--page-margin)
        calc(var(--space-6) + env(safe-area-inset-bottom));
    }

    .about-close {
      top: calc(var(--space-4) + env(safe-area-inset-top));
      right: calc(var(--page-margin) + var(--space-1));
    }

    .about-body {
      padding-inline: var(--space-2);
    }
  }
</style>
